full_text: Catching up on #AmericanSongContest and, ope, the block voting has started with Georgians voting for Alabama.  Traditions carry over from Europe!

There's an ad running on my preferred streaming service right now with a full audio slate in front of the actual ad, and I always feel a little better every time I hear it (because no one else has yet, I guess).
Live shot of how I am every day for the past year: https://t.co/bsMKFAY4Ju
